text: António Valente da Gama Bráz (born 8 December 1962) is a Portuguese equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Portugal Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Elvas
